21#ifndef GCC_LTO_TREE_H
22#define GCC_LTO_TREE_H
23
24struct GTY(()) lang_identifier
25{
26 struct tree_identifier base;
27};
28
29struct GTY(()) lang_decl
30{
31 int dummy; /* Added because ggc does not like empty structs. */
32};
33
34struct GTY(()) lang_type
35{
36 int dummy; /* Added because ggc does not like empty structs. */
37};
38
39struct GTY(()) language_function
40{
41 int dummy; /* Added because ggc does not like empty structs. */
42};
43
44enum lto_tree_node_structure_enum {
45 TS_LTO_GENERIC
46};
47
48union GTY((desc ("lto_tree_node_structure (&%h)"),
49 chain_next ("CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (TREE_CODE (&%h.generic), TS_TYPE_COMMON) ? ((union lang_tree_node *) %h.generic.type_common.next_variant) : CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (TREE_CODE (&%h.generic), TS_COMMON) ? ((union lang_tree_node *) %h.generic.common.chain) : NULL")))
50 lang_tree_node
51{
52 union tree_node GTY ((tag ("TS_LTO_GENERIC"),
53 desc ("tree_node_structure (&%h)"))) generic;
54};
55
56#endif /* GCC_LTO_TREE_H */
